Gaupol 0.13
===========

 [D] Raise PyGTK dependency to 2.12 or greater
 [D] Remove misuse of assertions that broke some parts of Gaupol, when
     used with Python's optimization (-O switch)
 [D] Preserve additional fields in SSA/ASS files
 [D] Preserve coordinate fields in extended SubRip format
 [ ] By default always use UTF-8 character encoding for preview
     (#522868, Beni Cherniavsky, Osmo Salomaa)
 [D] Allow comments (starting with number signs) in pattern files
 [D] Allow grouping of correction patterns under the same name
 [D] Improve commmon error patterns for spaces around quote marks
 [D] Allow reordering of columns
 [D] Resize columns when their visibility is toggled
 [D] Fix error with encoding auto-detection (#10278)
 [D] Fix error starting spell-check if no dictionary (#10526)
 [D] Fix preview error dialog if video player not found (#518981)
 [D] Fix subtitle number search after subtitle removals or inserts
 [D] Fix error displaying right-click menu in cells (kitone)
 [D] Fix IndexError with multiline tags in text cells (#547170)
 [D] Fix window type and transientness for preferences dialog
 [D] Fix error closing the search dialog from the window titlebar
 [D] Fix updating of Alt+NUM shortcut keys
 [D] Fix color markup tag conversions with various formats
 [D] Fix conversions of font tags with the SubRip format
 [D] Replace --adapt-translation option with --align-method
 [D] Add GenericName field to the desktop file
 [D] Add mimetypes application/x-subrip, text/x-microdvd,
     text/x-mpsub, text/x-ssa and text/x-subviewer to the desktop file
 [D] Fix spell-check language listing with recent versions of Enchant
 [D] Run 'update-desktop-database' in setup.py if --root not given
 [D] Move profile directory on Windows to %APPDATA%/Gaupol

 Note: The five digit bug numbers refer to the old bug tracker at Gna
 and the six digit ones to the new bug tracker at GNOME Bugzilla.


Gaupol 0.14
===========

 [?] Handle fancy quotes, dashes and ellipses in text corrections
     - As bogus regular expression groups?
       o (?gaupol-dash)
       o (?gaupol-quote)
       o (?gaupol-ellipsis)
 [?] Add notebooked panes to the side and bottom
 [?] Move the output window to the bottom pane
 [ ] Add an extension system
     - gaupol.gtk.Extension
     - gaupol.gtk.ExtensionManager
     - gaupol.gtk.PreferencesDialog
 [ ] Add an example extension (bookmark/notes column?)


Gaupol 1.0
==========

 * Add documentation on writing extensions
 * Add documentation on writing pattern files
 * Add a wiki page for publishing extensions
 * Add a wiki page for publishing pattern files


Gaupol 3000
===========

 * Migrate from Glade to gtk.Builder
 * Adher to freedesktop.org's XDG Base Directory Specification
 * Add built-in GStreamer preview (as plugin?)
 * Replace the headers-dialog with a more general properties-dialog
   - SubRip: Write coordinates (extended SubRip format)
   - MicroDVD: Write framerate information subtitle
 * PyGObject 2.16
   - Try gobject.option.OptionParser (see #378704)
   - Try gio.AppInfo for launching web browser and video player
 * PyEnchant 1.4
   - All dictionary providers now use a shared default personal word
     file (largely obsoleting the DictWithPWL class)
   - Dict.add_to_pwl renamed to Dict.add
